CAMERON
v.
UNIV. OF TOLEDO 2018-0592 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appeal and cross-appeal not accepted. O'Donnell, J., dissents and would accept the cross-appeal on proposition of law No. II. Kennedy and DeWine, JJ., dissent and would accept the appeal. Fischer, J, dissents and would accept the cross-appeal.
